@page "/"
@layout HomeLayout

<div class="canva-public-page">
    <section class="canva-hero">
        <div class="canva-hero__frame">
            <p class="canva-kicker">init · powered by JPV-OS · operated by JayPVentures LLC</p>
            <h1>Welcome to the Venture</h1>
            <p class="canva-lead">
                A unified access gateway for creators, members, partners, and enterprise operators moving through the JayPVentures ecosystem.
            </p>
            <div class="canva-actions">
                <a class="canva-button canva-button-primary" href="/pricing">View Access Options</a>
                <a class="canva-button canva-button-secondary" href="/ecosystem">Explore the Ecosystem</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="canva-section">
        <div class="canva-section__intro">
            <p class="canva-kicker">Ecosystem Architecture</p>
            <h2>One gateway. Multiple operational lanes.</h2>
            <p>
                init routes access into JPV-OS, JayPVentures LLC, jaypventures, jaypVLabs, and JPV Institute without flattening each entity into the same page template.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="canva-access-grid">
            <a href="/jaypventures-llc" class="canva-access-card"><span>Enterprise</span><strong>JayPVentures LLC</strong><p>Infrastructure, operations, security, and delivery authority.</p></a>
            <a href="/jaypventures" class="canva-access-card"><span>Creator</span><strong>jaypventures</strong><p>Venture studio, creator access, community, and adoption.</p></a>
            <a href="/jaypvlabs" class="canva-access-card"><span>Labs</span><strong>jaypVLabs</strong><p>Prototype validation, AI behavior, systems testing, and readiness.</p></a>
            <a href="/jpv-institute" class="canva-access-card"><span>Institute</span><strong>JPV Institute</strong><p>Doctrine, literacy, standards, research, and accreditation.</p></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="canva-section">
        <div class="canva-section__intro">
            <p class="canva-kicker">Access Gateway</p>
            <h2>Access that matches the role.</h2>
            <p>
                Member, VIP, creator, operator, enterprise, and sovereign paths connect payments, entitlements, and Discord access without forcing every user through the same experience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="canva-access-grid">
            <a href="/pricing" class="canva-access-card"><span>Members</span><strong>Member Access</strong><p>Community access, membership routing, and entry-level ecosystem participation.</p></a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="canva-access-card"><span>VIP</span><strong>VIP Venture</strong><p>Priority experiences, elevated community access, and venture-facing access lanes.</p></a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="canva-access-card"><span>Creator</span><strong>Creator Lane</strong><p>Creator tooling, monetization routing, and ecosystem growth support.</p></a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="canva-access-card"><span>Operator</span><strong>Operator</strong><p>Operational access for builders, moderators, implementation support, and delivery workflows.</p></a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="canva-access-card"><span>Enterprise</span><strong>Enterprise</strong><p>Partner packages, implementation visibility, infrastructure support, and governed delivery.</p></a>
            <a href="/contact" class="canva-access-card"><span>Sovereign</span><strong>Custom Access</strong><p>Custom architecture, private routing, and higher-governance implementation paths.</p></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="canva-section canva-founder">
        <div class="canva-founder__media">
            <div class="canva-founder__placeholder">JPV</div>
        </div>
        <div class="canva-founder__copy">
            <p class="canva-kicker">Founder Direction</p>
            <h2>Built to route access, infrastructure, and opportunity with operational integrity.</h2>
            <p>This gateway is the public entry point into creator access, enterprise delivery, community membership, partner routing, and governed infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="canva-final-cta">
        <p class="canva-kicker">Launch Path</p>
        <h2>Enter the ecosystem.</h2>
        <p>Choose the access lane that matches your role and move through the correct operational path.</p>
        <a class="canva-button canva-button-primary" href="/pricing">Get init</a>
    </section>
</div>
